  ---
  ADR 0001 — CHAP authentication: accepted but not implemented

  The ADR dated 2026-04-15 is marked Accepted. The decision was to add single shared CHAP credentials (chap_enabled, chap_user_name, chap_user_password) to the plugin. The current code has none of these: no properties declared, no CHAP parameters passed to jdssc targets create, no password file handling for CHAP credentials. The ADR consequence ("Volume start will get a bit slower") has not materialized. This is an open implementation gap.

